# tcs-git-helpers: v2.2.9
#
# One pattern per line; anchored to repo root; glob style.
#
# Patterns listed here are excluded from pre-commit hook checks
# (linting, format, autofixes). Anchored to repo root with ** for
# nested directories.
#
# Examples:
# .env.development
# tests/fixtures/*.env
# build/temp/*
# node_modules/
